00:36:14.590 --> 00:36:15.790
ay magiging mas malaki.

00:36:16.190 --> 00:36:17.840
Ngunit papayag kaya ang Empress Dowager?

00:36:17.840 --> 00:36:19.070
Talagang gagawin niya.

