Saka lang

00:36:24.960 --> 00:36:27.290
kailangan pa bang umasa sa kanya ni Xia Jingyan .

00:36:30.320 --> 00:36:31.980
Kailangan nating maghanda nang maaga.

00:36:32.430 --> 00:36:34.480
Oras na para magpadala ng salita sa Pingling City

00:36:34.480 --> 00:36:35.810
at tumawag ng mas maraming tao.

00:36:36.110 --> 00:36:36.840
Naintindihan.

